{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review how public services can be more Compassionate, Trauma-Informed & ND Aware",
        "additional_details": "Many aspects of life feel overwhelming with multiple \"Calls for evidence\" Instigated by the govt. I want all Public Facing public funded systems to at the very least offer an Empathetic, Compassionate, Caring response to those that they connect with, I would like this especially to be so within Doctors Surgery, NHS Wards and Clinics and that all administrators offer a level of care that supports emotions.",
        "background": " I want the government to undertake a review to better understand why many aspects of life may feel overwhelming for those who are ND, Care Experienced, or Unpaid Carers and recognise the many systems that may impact their Emotional and MH wellbeing. I want Care and Compassion to always be shown.",
